---
Source:
  Title: The Complete Works of Chuang Tzu
  ID: 50ae0a98-5702-40cb-8c11-4c6297aa457a
  Translator: Burton Watson
By: Zhuangzi
Locus:
  Chapter: 6
  Paragraph: 54
Title: The Great And Venerable Teacher
---
Yi Erh-tzu said, "Yao told me, `You must learn to practice benevolence
and righteousness and to speak clearly about right and wrong!'"
